channel.title: Auto loggin failure
channel.description: I have a problem with one of my scripts. Its an auto loggin script but for some reason it quits right before it logs in. It gets all the way to the login screen, and then it finishes. SOMEONE HELP!!! :( :( :(

item.title: Auto loggin failure
item.dc:creator: @Janilabo Janilabo
item.description:
@Janilabo wrote:

It compiles fine, at least.

Maybe something wrong with bitmaps? 8 bitmaps take 1100 lines. I can tell you, you have too big bitmaps. You should cut em a bit… But that MIGHT not be the reason it fails. Maybe it has something to do with wait times? I am not sure. I think the too big bitmaps causes problems. Like, it’s scanning for very huge things. From WHOLE screen.
